{"tid":2043001,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"阿仙奴主席退休　逾7成球迷想雲格繼任","createTime":"2020-05-30T06:35:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-31T04:53:39.000Z","uid":16659,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"5e797755b6c84ab220ca1043895d2ec6bd770f84","tid":2043001,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T06:35:17.000Z","msg":"阿仙奴80歲主席基斯域克爵士宣布，今季英超完結後將會退休，結束15年嘅「兵工廠」歲月。著名銀行家基斯域克喺2005年加入阿仙奴董事局，2013年正式出任球會主席，不過佢一向唔多參與球會日常運作，球隊事務目前都由足球主管辛尼爾同總監伊度負責。<br />\n<br />\n基斯域克爵士退休後，阿仙奴主席一職由邊個繼任未有定案，不過大批「廠迷」就喺網上呼籲，希望前領隊雲格可以回巢，佢哋認為雲格嘅管理能力一流，加上對阿仙奴嘅深厚認識，令佢成為主席一職最理想人選，英國《太陽報》調查顯示，有72.5%球迷贊成雲格做下任主席，只有18.8%球迷覺得唔應該再戀棧過去，8.7%球迷冇意見。"},{"pid":"9199422138a6aa7c7fac34a76fa51b69634c2485","tid":2043001,"uid":16659,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T06:36:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://gnayabchohan.files.wordpress.com/2018/05/5d34bf51-60a7-475c-a64c-f5cbdebdab17.gif?w=376\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgnayabchohan.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F05%2F5d34bf51-60a7-475c-a64c-f5cbdebdab17.gif%3Fw%3D376&h=4c04e5da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你值得擁有<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4258b8c160164b2b0d9a02a47faf268dab678bc2","tid":2043001,"uid":16659,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T06:36:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/7OX4pQmDcbV4fE4cse/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F7OX4pQmDcbV4fE4cse%2Fgiphy.gif&h=867ef0f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雲加繼任!"},{"pid":"86546375c8b0f5e9a78db9b6290d145258cab591","tid":2043001,"uid":16659,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T06:39:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://thumbs.gfycat.com/GrandBitterCobra-size_restricted.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumbs.gfycat.c